args: What's that you got there, Ranzal?
Ya picked out a gift for her too, eh?\nIn that case, which of us should go first?
I'll start. And lemme just say, I NAILED\nwhat Nefaria wants with this one.
Nefariaaaa! I have an amazing Dragonyule\ngift for yooooou!
And I shall accept it with gratitude.\n...Erm, my apologies, but there appears\nto be something in your hair.
Hmm? Oh yeah, you're right.\nLooks like a leaf decided to hitch a ride.
A leaf...? Did you go to the woods?
Yep! Had to wander preeetty far afield\nto find this little present.
Then you are giving her an item you\ncollected from the forest?
Does that not strike you as...\nWell, a bit odd?
Hey! I'm not gonna put all this effort into\nsomething just to give her a weirdo gift!

I got her some of this fruit that only grows
every few years, so it's super rare—er,
but now I've kinda spoiled the surprise,
so I might as well just hand it over.
It gladdens me to accept such a rare and\nprecious thing, Luca.
Sounds good to me! Er, so does that\nhelp you remember anything, or...?
I mean, if this is the thing you wanted,\nit should bring your memory back, right?
Alas, I fear those recollections are still but\na distant glimmer in my mind.
Guess you must have wanted something\ndifferent, then. Eh, whatcha gonna do?
Stand back, chumps—I got a gift what's\ngonna make Nefaria's eyes bug right\noutta her skull!
Someone is rather confident today.\nInspiration must have struck in the night.

Oh, I got inspiration comin' outta my...
Anyway, Nefaria's a former queen, yeah?
Which means she coulda had pretty much
whatever she wanted.
So I just tried to imagine something that\nshe COULDN'T have, even with all her\nroyal power and gold and whatnot.
That's actually a logical thought process.\n...Are you sure you're feeling all right?
Are you finished? Stop talking it up and\njust tell us what you got her already!
Yeah yeah, keep yer smallclothes on.\nMy present to Nefaria is...

BEEF! And not just any ol' beef—this is the
high-quality stuff where they feed the cows
caviar and chili all day or whatever.
It's almost impossible to find!
Check out the marblin' on this puppy!\nIt's practically a religious experience.
Er, guys? Why ain't ya baskin' in the glory\nof my beef?
Oh, we've no doubt as to the quality of\nthis item you procured.
I swear, the both of you have your brains\nlocated inside your stomachs.
Or you know what? I'll ask her myself.\nSo then! Was the thing you wanted most\nin the world a big hunk of dead cow?
Oh man, I was SO sure this was it!
Prithee do not mourn so, Ranzal.\nYour cut of meat looks delectable indeed.
Between this and Luca's fruit, I will be\nblessed with a fine meal this eve.
Thank you, Luca. Thank you, Ranzal.
Right then! Time to throw a feast!
A fine plan. Let us hurry forth and summon\n{player_name}.
I agree. Rather than saying she didn't like\nthose...wildly off-base gifts, she somehow\nmanaged to thank them profusely.
She has the tolerance of a true ruler.
I would expect no less of a former queen.
Yeah, fine. So we didn't exactly nail it—\nbut it ain't like you guys did neither!\nWhat does this lady even WANT?!
Well, it's clearly not fruit or beef, so...\nAha! Fish! It must be fish.
Yer a smart one, Luca—that's gotta be it!
Would the two of you PLEASE stop thinking\nabout food for one second?!
